///
/// "History"
@Node history "History of One Font"
 @{b}History@{ub}

 release 1.0 (version 37.1, 19/2/94)

    First release

 release 1.1 (version 37.2, 28/2/94)

    Name changed from MyFont to OneFont
    Shorter code (whole program 288 bytes instead of 336, resident part
       92 bytes instead of 174)
    Corrected mistake in installer script
    Corrected some mistakes in documentation
